WEBVTT

00:00:26.068 --> 00:00:31.280
hearing the plight
of a desperate slave father

00:00:31.280 --> 00:00:36.292
whose daughter was 
about to be sold to a brothel

00:00:36.302 --> 00:00:38.683
made me angry.

00:00:40.423 --> 00:00:42.763
At the age of 50,

00:00:42.763 --> 00:00:47.586
lying on the street,
in a pool of blood,

00:00:47.586 --> 00:00:50.532
along with my own son,

00:00:50.532 --> 00:00:52.999
made me angry.

00:00:55.299 --> 00:01:00.484
Dear friends, for centuries
we were taught anger is bad.